FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1780517152
OL,3,CBody found in search for missing 11-
OL,4,Cyear-old near Mexborough
OL,6,FIn a statement, South Yorkshire
OL,7,FPolice, said: "Mackenzie had last been
OL,8,Fseen entering the River Don near
OL,9,FMexborough on Saturday evening, and
OL,10,Fthe alarm was raided when he was not
OL,11,Fseen to emerge."
OL,13,FThey added: "Mackenzie's family have
OL,14,Fbeen informed and have the offer of
OL,15,Fspecialist support. Formal
OL,16,Fidentification will take place in due
OL,17,Fcourse."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1780517152
OL,3,CBody found in search for missing 11-
OL,4,Cyear-old near Mexborough
OL,6,FChief Superintendent Pete Thorp ` the
OL,7,Fdistrict commander for Doncaster,
OL,8,Fsaid: "First and foremost, on behalf
OL,9,Fof all who have been involved in the
OL,10,Foperation to find Mackenzie since
OL,11,FSaturday, I send deepest sympathies to
OL,12,Fhis family and friends.
OL,14,F"Losing a child is every parent's
OL,15,Fworst nightmare and I know the impact
OL,16,Fthis news will have on the wider
OL,17,Fcommunity and particularly Mackenzie's
OL,18,Fschool.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1780517152
OL,3,CBody found in search for missing 11-
OL,4,Cyear-old near Mexborough
OL,6,F"The search for Mackenzie has been a
OL,7,Freal multi-agency effort and, while
OL,8,FSYP are thankful to our emergency
OL,9,Fservice colleagues and the underwater
OL,10,Fsearch team, I would like to take a
OL,11,Fmoment to recognise Woodhead Mountain
OL,12,FRescue.
OL,14,F"While highly trained and skilled,
OL,15,Fmany of their team are volunteers who
OL,16,Fgive up their time to help search
OL,17,Fteams when they need it most.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1780517152
OL,3,CBody found in search for missing 11-
OL,4,Cyear-old near Mexborough
OL,6,F"I would also like to thank the local
OL,7,Fcommunity, who enabled us to conduct
OL,8,Four search and recovery with very few
OL,9,Fonlookers and cameras to give
OL,10,FMackenzie and his family the dignity
OL,11,Fthey deserve.
OL,13,F"Not only for that, but also for the
OL,14,Foffers of assistance - we knew we had
OL,15,Fmany members of the public willing to
OL,16,Fdo anything they could to help."
OL,18,FIt follows a number of other water-
OL,19,Frelated deaths across the country
OL,20,Famidst a spell of hot weather.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
